
'''Kereke ya Evangheli ya vu Presbethari e Afrika Dzonga''' ( kumbe '''Vurhumiwa bya Swisi''' ) i kereke ya vukhongeri bya vukreste eka xi yenge xa vu phurotestanti.

Kereke leyi yi na vuxaka na tikereke leti hundzulukeke e tikweni ra Switzerland.Â Kereke leyi yi vumbiwa hi marhavi manharhu: Kereke ya muganga, Ntlawa wa Vafundhisi va xifundza, Huvo leyi fumaka ya kereke.<ref>[http://www.epcsa.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=148&Itemid=581]. Evangelical Presbyterian Church in South Africa.</ref> Kereke leyi yi na mintlwa ya nkombo ya swi fundza.<ref>[http://www.epcsa.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=150&Itemid=585]. Evangelical Presbyterian Church in South Africa.</ref>

Kereke leyi i xirho xa Vukwetsimi bya ti kereke ta misava leti hundzulukeke (World Communion of Reformed Churches).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wcrc.ch/wcrc-member-churches/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=19 May 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221035027/http://wcrc.ch/wcrc-member-churches/ |archivedate=21 December 2013 }}. [[World Communion of Reformed Churches]].</ref> Kereke leyi yi tshunelene no tirhisana na Kereke ya Presbetari ya Muzambhiki na Kereke ya evangheli ya Lesotho.

Kereke leyi yi tiyisa Xiboho xa va Apostola (kumbe vunharhu vun'we) na xiboho xa Naysini (Vupfumeri bya vukreste).<ref>[http://www.epcsa.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=145&Itemid=575]. Evangelical Presbyterian Church in South Africa.</ref>

Hi lembe ra 2004, kereke leyi a yiri na 30,000 wa malandza, 37 wa tinhlengeletano na 7 wa miti ya vugandzeri. Ririmi ra ximfumo ra kereke leyi i [[xitsonga]].<ref>[http://www.reformiert-online.net/adressen/detail.php?id=13279&lg=eng]. Reformed Online.</ref>

